# Table 2: __and__ / __rand__ / __iand__ dict-presence (set-intersection)
#
# Checks islice, repeat, starmap, compress, dropwhile, filterfalse — all False.
# Lazy iterators do not implement the set-intersection protocol.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

